blindness and dysgraphia.

00:02:09.960 --> 00:02:11.640
I have a story.

00:02:12.960 --> 00:02:14.719
Hearing with only one ear,

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:20.079
it's impossible for me to identify
where sounds are coming from.

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:21.839
After about a month of dating,

00:02:21.840 --> 00:02:25.799
we went for a walk on a beautiful island
by the Danube.

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:27.599
We heard music playing.

00:02:27.600 --> 00:02:30.493
My wife asked, "What's that sound?"

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:35.639
I said to her, "If you can tell
me where it's coming from,

00:02:35.640 --> 00:02:38.360
I can tell you what it is."

00:02:39.240 --> 00:02:43.199
This story represents
the connection between people.

00:02:43.200 --> 00:02:47.040
We need to work
together to get things done.

00:02:47.880 --> 00:02:51.119
This experience tells
me that collaboration

00:02:51.120 --> 00:02:53.920
is key to overcoming challenges.

00:02:54.520 --> 00:02:56.879
Accessibility is no different.

00:02:56.880 --> 00:03:00.599
It's about creating
an environment where everyone,

00:03:00.600 --> 00:03:07.520
regardless of their abilities,
can participate fully and independently.

00:03:08.376 --> 00:03:12.719
Whether it's navigating
a website or booking a seat at a concert,

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:16.239
accessibility ensures
that everyone can get

00:03:16.240 --> 00:03:20.320
things done efficiently and in dignity.

00:03:21.360 --> 00:03:23.160
Just picture this.

00:03:23.396 --> 00:03:27.879
A user asks a computer for available
seats in a music hall.

00:03:27.880 --> 00:03:31.559
The designer would write
squares with an X inside for booked

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:36.320
seats and green squares
with a dot inside for available ones.

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:39.960
This is inclusive for everybody.

00:03:40.400 --> 00:03:43.919
Even the color-blind user
can select a free seat

00:03:43.920 --> 00:03:49.200
because not only the color but
the dot inside makes them different.

00:03:51.320 --> 00:03:53.000
Learning objectives.

00:03:54.405 --> 00:03:58.769
We have three practical
outcomes from this presentation.

00:03:59.280 --> 00:04:00.879
First of all,

00:04:00.880 --> 00:04:07.279
