cannot be accessible.

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:12.600
I offer a fresh look and show
a new way of designing a website.

00:04:13.080 --> 00:04:17.039
Second, we the experts overemphasize

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:21.007
the Web Content Accessibility
Guidelines, the WCAG.

00:04:21.320 --> 00:04:23.840
It's a standard, not a method.

00:04:24.040 --> 00:04:28.860
The success criteria is important,
but even more important

00:04:29.220 --> 00:04:32.880
to know your users
with different abilities.

00:04:33.880 --> 00:04:37.119
In addition,
many people think that it's enough

00:04:37.120 --> 00:04:40.373
to comply with the law by using a plugin.

00:04:40.640 --> 00:04:45.321
If you have a trendy website,
why would you need an overlay?

00:04:45.880 --> 00:04:49.439
Accessibility comes
from a website owner's strategy

00:04:49.440 --> 00:04:52.959
called Accessibility In Mind.

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:56.959
If you succeed,
your site will be available

00:04:56.960 --> 00:04:58.799
to users with disabilities.

00:04:58.800 --> 00:05:02.059
In addition, the majority of your users

00:05:02.060 --> 00:05:06.120
will get an even better user experience.

